<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>An applicant may seek credit through the AP program by submitting an official record of scores to the Admissions Office. Credit is granted for scores of 3 or above. Credit earned through AP will not count toward the Bay Path residency requirement.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.baypath.edu/Academics/CourseCatalog.aspx" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
